        "CharacterDialogInfo_List": [
          {
            "CharacterId": 10050,
            "CostumeUniqueId": 1005001,
            "DisplayOrder": 300,
            "DialogCategory": 8,
            "DialogCondition": 0,
            "GroupId": 1,
            "ActionName": "",
            "DialogType": 0,
            "Duration": 10667,
            "LocalizeKR": "그래도……\n제가 당근을 싫어하는 게\n변하는 건 아니에요.",
            "LocalizeJP": "その……別に、ニンジンを\n好きになったわけでは\nありませんからね。",
            "VoiceIds": [],
            "CollectionVisible": false,
            "CVCollectionType": 0,
            "LocalizeCVGroup": "CVGroup_UILobbySpecial_Idle1",
            "AnimationName": "Talk_01_M",
            "Anniversary": 0,
            "StartDate": "",
            "EndDate": "",
            "ApplyPosition": false,
            "PosX": 0.0,
            "PosY": 0.0,
            "UnlockFavorRank": 0,
            "UnlockEquipWeapon": false
          },
          {
            "CharacterId": 10050,
            "CostumeUniqueId": 1005001,
            "DisplayOrder": 310,
            "DialogCategory": 8,
            "DialogCondition": 0,
            "GroupId": 2,
            "ActionName": "",
            "DialogType": 0,
            "Duration": 9000,
            "LocalizeKR": "모처럼 선생님과 오기도 했고,\n어엿한 교관이니까 어쩔 수 없이\n먹고 있을 뿐이에요.",
            "LocalizeJP": "せっかく先生と一緒に来た\nわけですし、一人前の教官として\n仕方なく食べているだけです。",
            "VoiceIds": [],
            "CollectionVisible": false,
            "CVCollectionType": 0,
            "LocalizeCVGroup": "CVGroup_UILobbySpecial_Idle2",
            "AnimationName": "Talk_02_M",
            "Anniversary": 0,
            "StartDate": "",
            "EndDate": "",
            "ApplyPosition": false,
            "PosX": 0.0,
            "PosY": 0.0,
            "UnlockFavorRank": 0,
            "UnlockEquipWeapon": false
          },
          {
            "CharacterId": 10050,
            "CostumeUniqueId": 1005001,
            "DisplayOrder": 320,
            "DialogCategory": 8,
            "DialogCondition": 0,
            "GroupId": 2,
            "ActionName": "",
            "DialogType": 0,
            "Duration": 13833,
            "LocalizeKR": "아시겠어요?\n정말, 선생님은\n언제나 억지로……",
            "LocalizeJP": "分かりましたか？\n全く、先生はいつも\n無理やり……。",
            "VoiceIds": [],
            "CollectionVisible": false,
            "CVCollectionType": 0,
            "LocalizeCVGroup": "CVGroup_UILobbySpecial_Idle2",
            "AnimationName": "",
            "Anniversary": 0,
            "StartDate": "",
            "EndDate": "",
            "ApplyPosition": false,
            "PosX": 0.0,
            "PosY": 0.0,
            "UnlockFavorRank": 0,
            "UnlockEquipWeapon": false
          },
          {
            "CharacterId": 10050,
            "CostumeUniqueId": 1005001,
            "DisplayOrder": 330,
            "DialogCategory": 8,
            "DialogCondition": 0,
            "GroupId": 3,
            "ActionName": "",
            "DialogType": 0,
            "Duration": 10333,
            "LocalizeKR": "만약 당근을 반드시\n먹어야 하는 경우라면……\n다음부터는, 여기로 올 거에요.",
            "LocalizeJP": "もしどうしてもニンジンを\n食べないといけない場合は……\n今度からは、ここに来ます。",
            "VoiceIds": [],
            "CollectionVisible": false,
            "CVCollectionType": 0,
            "LocalizeCVGroup": "CVGroup_UILobbySpecial_Idle3",
            "AnimationName": "Talk_03_M",
            "Anniversary": 0,
            "StartDate": "",
            "EndDate": "",
            "ApplyPosition": false,
            "PosX": 0.0,
            "PosY": 0.0,
            "UnlockFavorRank": 0,
            "UnlockEquipWeapon": false
          },
          {
            "CharacterId": 10050,
            "CostumeUniqueId": 1005001,
            "DisplayOrder": 340,
            "DialogCategory": 8,
            "DialogCondition": 0,
            "GroupId": 4,
            "ActionName": "",
            "DialogType": 0,
            "Duration": 7000,
            "LocalizeKR": "선생님과 처음\n함께 온 장소, 이기도 하고……",
            "LocalizeJP": "先生と一緒に来たお店、\nということもありますし……",
            "VoiceIds": [],
            "CollectionVisible": false,
            "CVCollectionType": 0,
            "LocalizeCVGroup": "CVGroup_UILobbySpecial_Idle4",
            "AnimationName": "Talk_04_M",
            "Anniversary": 0,
            "StartDate": "",
            "EndDate": "",
            "ApplyPosition": false,
            "PosX": 0.0,
            "PosY": 0.0,
            "UnlockFavorRank": 0,
            "UnlockEquipWeapon": false
          },
          {
            "CharacterId": 10050,
            "CostumeUniqueId": 1005001,
            "DisplayOrder": 350,
            "DialogCategory": 8,
            "DialogCondition": 0,
            "GroupId": 4,
            "ActionName": "",
            "DialogType": 0,
            "Duration": 9500,
            "LocalizeKR": "아시겠어요? 좋아하게\n된 게 아니라구요?\n아시겠죠?",
            "LocalizeJP": "良いですか？\n好きになってはないですよ？\n分かってます？",
            "VoiceIds": [],
            "CollectionVisible": false,
            "CVCollectionType": 0,
            "LocalizeCVGroup": "CVGroup_UILobbySpecial_Idle4",
            "AnimationName": "",
            "Anniversary": 0,
            "StartDate": "",
            "EndDate": "",
            "ApplyPosition": false,
            "PosX": 0.0,
            "PosY": 0.0,
            "UnlockFavorRank": 0,
            "UnlockEquipWeapon": false
          },
          {
            "CharacterId": 10050,
            "CostumeUniqueId": 1005001,
            "DisplayOrder": 360,
            "DialogCategory": 8,
            "DialogCondition": 0,
            "GroupId": 5,
            "ActionName": "",
            "DialogType": 0,
            "Duration": 12500,
            "LocalizeKR": "뭐……\n당근도, 그렇게까지\n나쁘지는 않네요.",
            "LocalizeJP": "ただまあ……\nニンジンも、そこまで悪くは\nないかもしれません。",
            "VoiceIds": [],
            "CollectionVisible": false,
            "CVCollectionType": 0,
            "LocalizeCVGroup": "CVGroup_UILobbySpecial_Idle5",
            "AnimationName": "Talk_05_M",
            "Anniversary": 0,
            "StartDate": "",
            "EndDate": "",
            "ApplyPosition": false,
            "PosX": 0.0,
            "PosY": 0.0,
            "UnlockFavorRank": 0,
            "UnlockEquipWeapon": false
          }
        ],
